window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Tom Thorne is back...and so is his worst nightmare.</b></p> <p><b>Tom Thorne has it all.</b></p> <p>In Nicola Tanner and Phil Hendricks, Thorne has good friends by his side. He finally has a love life worth a damn and is happy in the job to which he has devoted his life....</p> <p><b>He has everything to lose.</b></p> <p>Hunting the woman responsible for a series of grisly murders, Thorne has no way of knowing that he will be plunged into a nightmare from which he may never wake.</p> <p><b>And he'll do anything to keep it.</b></p> <p>Finally, Thorne's past has caught up with him and a ruinous secret is about to be revealed. If he wants to save himself and his friends, he must do the unthinkable.</p>"; 
